##################################
##################################
# THE LINE OF OTGER CATALON or AUTHARIUS CATHALO, aka AUDEGAR GOLANS
# Bane of the Moors, Hammer of Infidels
# He is supposedly the same person as Eudes the Great of Aquitaine,
# but given that in here the Kings of Aquitaine are Goths, then I think it's better
# to make this twist and focus on this legend. Audegar was, after all, a Goth.
# He also is said to descend from St Parsifal and King Pellinor, who died at the Catalaunic Fields (or Battle of Chalons).
##################################
# Kings of Aquitaine #############
##################################
#1720100-
##################################
##################################
#
